-- Italy’s Danieli Eyes CMC’s Iron Mills in Croatia, Poslovni Says
-- B y   J a s m i n a   K u z m a n o v i c
-- 2012-05-21T09:22:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-21/italy-s-danieli-eyes-cmc-s-iron-mills-in-croatia-poslovni-says.html
A unit of Danieli SpA, a global
manufacturer of iron- and steel-making plants, is interested in
purchasing Croatian iron mills CMC Sisak d.o.o., a unit of U.S.
 Commercial Metals Co. (CMC) ,  Poslovni Dnevnik  reported today, without
saying where it got the information.  Representatives of Acciaierie Bertoli Safau, a steelmaking
division of Danieli, last week visited the mills in Sisak,
according to Poslovni Dnevnik.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jasmina Kuzmanovic in Zagreb at 
 jkuzmanovic@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
